        { q: 'Which areas in Kanpur do you cover?', a: 'We cover all areas across Kanpur and surrounding regions including residential, commercial, and industrial zones.' },
        { q: 'Is your pest control service safe for kids and pets in Kanpur?', a: 'Yes! All treatments in Kanpur use WHO-approved, government-certified, low-toxicity products that are safe for families, children, and pets.' },
        { q: 'How do I book pest control in Kanpur?', a: 'Call us, WhatsApp us, or fill the online form above. We confirm appointments in Kanpur within 30 minutes.' }
